source.name: Curb Ramps
source.description:
SF Curb Ramps - Locations and potential locations of curb ramps in the City and County of San Francisco.
Data is from San Francisco's Department of Public Works Curb Ramp Information System (CRIS) on June 25, 2012 at 3:47pm.

Geographic Coordinate System: WGS84 Lat Long.
